	author = {Dujon, Bernard and Sherman, David and Fischer, Gilles and Durrens, Pascal and Casaregola, Serge and Lafontaine, Ingrid and de Montigny, Jacky and Marck, Christian and Neuvéglise, Cécile and Talla, Emmanuel and Goffard, Nicolas and Frangeul, Lionel and Aigle, Michel and Anthouard, Véronique and Babour, Anna and Barbe, Valérie and Barnay, Stéphanie and Blanchin, Sylvie and Beckerich, Jean-Marie and Beyne, Emmanuelle and Bleykasten, Claudine and Boisramé, Anita and Boyer, Jeanne and Cattolico, Laurence and Confanioleri, Fabrice and de Daruvar, Antoine and Despons, Laurence and Fabre, Emmanuelle and Fairhead, Cécile and Ferry-Dumazet, Hélène and Groppi, Alexis and Hantraye, Florence and Hennequin, Christophe and Jauniaux, Nicolas and Joyet, Philippe and Kachouri, Rym and Kerrest, Alix and Koszul, Romain and Lemaire, Marc and Lesur, Isabelle and Ma, Laurence and Muller, Héloïse and Nicaud, Jean-Marc and Nikolski, Macha and Oztas, Sophie and Ozier-Kalogeropoulos, Odile and Pellenz, Stefan and Potier, Serge and Richard, Guy-Franck and Straub, Marie-Laure and Suleau, Audrey and Swennen, Dominique and Tekaia, Fredj and Wésolowski-Louvel, Micheline and Westhof, Eric and Wirth, Bénédicte and Zeniou-Meyer, Maria and Zivanovic, Ivan and Bolotin-Fukuhara, Monique and Thierry, Agnès and Bouchier, Christiane and Caudron, Bernard and Scarpelli, Claude and Gaillardin, Claude and Weissenbach, Jean and Wincker, Patrick and Souciet, Jean-Luc},
